room_title: Escape room "Escaping Wonderland" by Escape Room 207 in Brunswick
room_description: Your friend Alice keeps telling you stories about an interesting place she keeps visiting. Stories that sound so unreal, that there is no way she is making it up. Stories about queens and kings, cats and caterpillars. Her most recent story was very intriguing, her friend The Hare has been convicted of painting the roses red, a huge no-no in this land. The Hatter claims he saw who actually did but does not dare to go to the queen without more evidence. Alice wasn’t sure she could do this on her own and asked if you’d be willing to help. With the clues laid out by the Hatter can you help save the Hare from losing his head and escape wonderland before you lose yours as well.
